Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/bchifu/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule add <plugin> pack/bchifu/start/<plugin_name>
    git add .gitmodules vim/pack/bchifu/start/<plugin_name>
    git commit

To update plugins:

    git submodule update --remote --merge
    git commit

To remove plugins:

   git submodule deinit ~/.vim/pack/bchifu/start/<plugin_name>
   git rm ~/.vim/pack/bchifu/start/<plugin_name>
   rm -Rf ~/vim/.git/modules/pack/bchifu/start/<plugin_name>
   git commit
